{
  "texts": [
    "Significantly more technical literature exists on AI in general.",
    "The spectrum includes works on information technology, the impacts of AI application in various areas (economy, industry, etc.",
    "), as well as cultural, psychological, philosophical, and particularly ethical questions (e.g., Chen, 2023; Gupta et al., 2023; Lapidus, 2023; Rakowski et al., 2023; Ullmann, 1965).",
    "Unfortunately, there still lacks scientific literature about ChatGPT and psychology/psychotherapy (Uludag, 2023), but some papers have been published on related issues.",
    "For example, Javaid et al. (2023) cite application areas for ChatGPT in healthcare such as patient education, clinical trial support, access to health-related information, counseling, symptom and syndrome recognition support, treatment program development, and individual health counseling."
  ]
}